on China-Africa myself

00:01:57.820 --> 00:02:00.310
and to share some of the
lessons from my research

00:02:00.310 --> 00:02:01.910
with you today.

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:03.380
So to start us off,

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:05.360
I brought you a video from the forum

